org.openlcb

Class Message

Show UML class diagram
  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openlcb.Message
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OpenLcb
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AddressedMessage, ConsumerIdentifiedMessage, IdentifyConsumersMessage, IdentifyProducersMessage, InitializationCompleteMessage, LearnEventMessage, ProducerConsumerEventReportMessage, ProducerIdentifiedMessage, VerifiedNodeIDNumberMessage, VerifyNodeIDNumberMessage

    @Immutable
 @ThreadSafe
public abstract class Message
extends Object
implements OpenLcb
    Base for all OpenLCB message types

    Messages (and therefore all subtypes) are immutable once created.

    A Message works with a MessageDecoder object in a double dispatch pattern to do message specific-processing in e.g. a node implementation.

    See Also:
    MessageDecoder
